{"tid":1952631,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"少一分批評 多一分稱讚","createTime":"2020-03-31T17:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T04:08:38.000Z","uid":54564,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5696864ca0214f74fd885c6390cb5e7a312ffbe3","tid":1952631,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:05:48.000Z","msg":"今日睇咗Netflix一套documentary &ldquo;100 humans&rdquo;嘅其中一集<br />\n當中做咗個實驗 係揾一批人去學習轉碟 <br />\n學完之後會被老師評審<br />\n<br />\n老師每評一個之前都會抽一粒波 <br />\n去決定佢要<span style=\"color: gold;\">讚</span> or <span style=\"color: red;\">彈</span> 嗰位學生 <br />\n無論佢做得好定唔好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q7iv7kc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ7iv7kc.png&h=413c9213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kWdoHTE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkWdoHTE.png&h=b4e99705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5VOHd0r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VOHd0r.png&h=980d5cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cd6d47d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcd6d47d.png&h=7225f1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yyODwNn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyyODwNn.png&h=b2b930be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyPy48o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyPy48o.png&h=dece17ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZO2wROw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZO2wROw.png&h=72b6049f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第1round被讚之後有<span style=\"color: gold;\">明顯進步</span><br />\n心情都明顯係好咗 笑容滿臉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BXDzPAi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBXDzPAi.png&h=4bccc7e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6osEgfr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6osEgfr.png&h=54482bcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1HYW2Vy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1HYW2Vy.png&h=d77213ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVz7qav.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVz7qav.png&h=d61bb36a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVqePCi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVqePCi.png&h=64e012d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eqVa7o5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeqVa7o5.png&h=c1fbc4ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NF9GuCx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNF9GuCx.png&h=4150ab03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/om3oHXG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fom3oHXG.png&h=7c91d4fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而被批評嘅人 喺第2round會<span style=\"color: red;\">退步</span><br />\n心情明顯差咗 閪曬臉 又會諗好多嘢 甚至質疑自己<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Ymaosk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Ymaosk.png&h=e05802b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VyMaost.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVyMaost.png&h=34c58ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LtbhNUg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLtbhNUg.png&h=75c4d36a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJuOUzp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBJuOUzp.png&h=609ff60d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nTTzP7O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnTTzP7O.png&h=865fab9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZAeP7T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZAeP7T.png&h=8bc393c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0SHY1i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0SHY1i.png&h=ccbbb10f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n套用番喺日常生活上<br />\n唔係需要你好似個實驗咁盲目去讚賞對方<br />\n或者盲目咁認同對方<br />\n<br />\n只係希望大家對住同路人嘅時候<span style=\"color: gold;\">多一分包容</span><br />\n就算大家可能喺目標上未有一致嘅決定 <br />\n(體制內外鬥爭之辨)<br />\n<br />\n都可以<span style=\"color: gold;\">互相尊重對方</span>做法<br />\n<br />\n記得我哋無分化嘅本錢 <br />\n記得8 9月我哋成日嗌要<span style=\"color: gold;\">be humble</span><br />\n我哋需要多一點<span style=\"color: gold;\">正能量</span>去扶持大家<br />\n一齊喺呢條革命嘅道路上行落去<br />\n<br />\n黑警藍絲就屌柒佢老母臭閪死全家啦"},{"pid":"5487e18927b2ddde6c850b0f0d63c4a921c44def","tid":1952631,"uid":54564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:07:49.000Z","msg":"其實一直都唔少手足講過<br />\n預期大大力批評手足<br />\n不如試下轉個語氣鼓勵下手足"},{"pid":"d86f0c1d56cae4885ce2488e075926b51699e309","tid":1952631,"uid":54564,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"屌得多甚至會形成一種逆向嘅叛逆心理<br />\n相信大家都試過明明本身已經準備去做某樣嘢<br />\n例如去溫書<br />\n但當你媽子命令你 / 語氣好差咗要求你去溫書嘅時候<br />\n你第一反應多數都係好不滿<br />\n<br />\n「我係都唔溫啊 吹咩」嘅心態<br />\n<br />\n將心比心<br />\n無乜人天生鐘意受你氣<br />\n所以無必要下下一嚟就嘈人"},{"pid":"36a92c8ecdcf5dd04103574af7801e12d4ec6b7e","tid":1952631,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d86f0c1d56cae4885ce2488e075926b51699e309","tid":1952631,"uid":54564,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"屌得多甚至會形成一種逆向嘅叛逆心理<br />\n相信大家都試過明明本身已經準備去做某樣嘢<br />\n例如去溫書<br />\n但當你媽子命令你 / 語氣好差咗要求你去溫書嘅時候<br />\n你第一反應多數都係好不滿<br />\n<br />\n「我係都唔溫啊 吹咩」嘅心態<br />\n<br />\n將心比心<br />\n無乜人天生鐘意受你氣<br />\n所以無必要下下一嚟就嘈人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />溫書好辛苦<br />\n可唔可以讚下我"},{"pid":"09a428d963fe97efb4e2903b6d840d6b84446e80","tid":1952631,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T18:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n絶對認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時有 6 個正評(我未畀),  但係就只得一個回覆,<br />\n大家係咪咁內歛 ?<br />\n<br />\n要多一分稱讚呀"},{"pid":"bd03935ad8289886237f31eb93c97551916ce164","tid":1952631,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09a428d963fe97efb4e2903b6d840d6b84446e80","tid":1952631,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T18:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n絶對認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時有 6 個正評(我未畀),  但係就只得一個回覆,<br />\n大家係咪咁內歛 ?<br />\n<br />\n要多一分稱讚呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T18:21:13.000Z","msg":"原來畀咗,  第6個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係我畀既"},{"pid":"43dbafa67d4a26117d012cbd7286a620b9e3a7ac","tid":1952631,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c